title: Number of active physicians in Alabama 2019 , by specialty area
summary: This bar chart has 10 categories for the x axis representing Specialty area, and a y axis representing Number of physicians.
The highest category is found at Total_specialty where Number of physicians is 6342.0.
The lowest category is found at Endocrinology_diabetes_&_metabolism where Number of physicians is 71.0.
gold: This statistic depicts the number of active physicians in Alabama as of March 2019 , sorted by specialty area . In that year , there were 602 anesthesiologists active in Alabama . Thus , this was one of the three largest specialty groups in Alabama .
